snippet.title: Morphle and the Dinosaurs (+1 hour funny Morphle kids videos compilation with cars, trucks, bus etc)
snippet.description:
In this compilation of the My Magic Pet Morphle cartoon, Morphle morphs into dinosaurs and then into all sorts of other things like vehicles, animals, and a robot

Subscribe to Morphle TV Here: https://www.youtube.com/user/MagicPetsSongs4Kids?sub_confirmation=1

Check out more from My Magic Pet Morphle: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmwpvieHKxgFq02SdiE9QlKexrSZYQajA

'My Magic Pet Morphle' is an animated hit tv show for toddlers and older kids. But because of its fun colors and sounds, it is even popular with babies. Morphle can morph into anything his human companion Mila wants. From dinosaurs to cars, construction vehicles like diggers, dump trucks, and cranes to pets like cats dogs, and lions! All our episodes have an educational core to them so that your kids can learn about things like shapes, numbers, and colors.

snippet.title: Morphle the dinosaur goes back in time!
snippet.description:
Morphle Playlist:  https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmwpvieHKxgF2A7612PdKabO1EEjfe5aP This is a compilation of the 'My Magic Pet Morphle' children's cartoon series. Morphle the magic superhero can morph into all sorts of dinosaurs and meets a real life T-rex. When they find a surprise mystery egg Mila and Morphle try to find which dinosaur the egg belongs to!

My Magic Pet Morphle is a fun TV show for toddlers and older kids, but because of it's fun colors and sounds it is even popular with babies. 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Bandits in the Age of the Dinosaurs: Directed by: Mark Bastiaan

Produced by: Arthur van Merwijk

Morphle Credits:

Mila: Sabrina Glow ( http://www.glowgirlskidvoiceover.com )

Animation: Danne Bakker, Mark Bastiaan, Nicole Derksen, Jessy Suharyanto, Jesse Tamerius, Merel Hamers, Etienne van Emden, Ruben Zaalberg, Jeroen Koffeman

Backgrounds: Jan-Jaap Schraverus

Character Designs: Jan Jaap Schraverus, Stein Louisse , David Muchtar


Rigging: Stein Louisse, Jeroen Koffeman, David Muchtar, Jan Jaap Schraverus, Jesse Tamerius

Sound Design & Music: Spoon-sound 
( http://www. spoon-sound.com )

MORPH:
Fans of Aardman Animations may remember Morph, the loveable clay character who lived on Tony Hart's desk and could change into lots of different shapes! 

NEW MORPH:
After an amazing response from the public, Morph creator and Aardman co-founder Peter Lord launched a campaign to bring Morph back for a new series of adventures! Using the crowd-funding website Kickstarter, Peter appealed to fans to help Morph make a comeback in return for a host of exclusive rewards and the chance to be involved in the production process. 
These new episodes will all premiere on YouTube.

snippet.title: Morphle Morphs Into Mila - My Magic Pet Morphle | Cartoons For Kids | Morphle TV
snippet.description:
Enjoy This Morphle and friends special compilation featuring some of your favourite My Magic Pet Morphle episodes including 'Morphle Morphs Into Mila '.
Subscribe to Morphle TV Here: https://www.youtube.com/user/MagicPetsSongs4Kids?sub_confirmation=1

In this compilation of the My Magic Pet Morphle cartoon Morphle morphs into all sorts of things like a T-Rex, Dinosaurs, Triceratops,  an Ambulance, Monster Truck, a truck, a dump truck a fire truck, bus, a crane. other vehicles, dinosaurs, animals and a robot.

'My Magic Pet Morphle' is an animated hit tv show for toddlers and older kids. But because of it's fun colors and sounds it is even popular with babies. Morphle can morph into anything his human companion Mila wants. From dinosaus to cars, construction vehicles like diggers, dumptrucks and cranes to pets like cats dogs and lions! All our episodes have an educational core to them so that your kids can learn about things like shapes, numbers and colors.

snippet.title: The End of Morphe (class action lawsuit)
snippet.description:
The End of Morphe (class action lawsuit) for years now influencers such as Jaclyn Hill and James Charles have been making palettes with the brand Morphe. Many different complaints about Morphe have arisen over the years about the quality of their products as well as the honesty of the people that support the brand. Now, a class action lawsuit has been filed in the state of California that is 52 pages long. in this video i'll read you the classaction.org article as well as link you to it and the lawsuit documents. let me know your thoughts down below. 

if you would like to inquire about this lawsuit you can reach out to the attorney's listed here.

MILBERG COLEMAN BRYSON

Beverly Hills, CA 90212
(917) 471-1894 (phone)
(615) 921-6501 (fax)

snippet.title: Ice Cream Morphle | My Magic Pet Morphle | Cartoons for Kids | Morphle TV
snippet.description:
Enjoy This Morphle and friends special compilation featuring some of your favourite My Magic Pet Morphle episodes including 'Morphle Eats Too Much Ice Cream, Morphle Morphs Into Mila, Mila and Morphle have a fight and more'.
Subscribe to Morphle TV Here: https://www.youtube.com/user/MagicPetsSongs4Kids?sub_confirmation=1

In this compilation of the My Magic Pet Morphle cartoon Morphle morphs into all sorts of things like a T-Rex, Dinosaurs, Triceratops,  an Ambulance, Monster Truck, a truck, a dump truck a fire truck, bus, a crane. other vehicles, dinosaurs, animals and a robot.

'My Magic Pet Morphle' is an animated hit tv show for toddlers and older kids. But because of it's fun colors and sounds it is even popular with babies. Morphle can morph into anything his human companion Mila wants. From dinosaus to cars, construction vehicles like diggers, dumptrucks and cranes to pets like cats dogs and lions! All our episodes have an educational core to them so that your kids can learn about things like shapes, numbers and colors.

snippet.title: Bad Morphle - Halloween | My Magic Pet Morphle | Cartoons For Kids | Morphle TV
snippet.description:
Enjoy This Morphle and friends special compilation featuring some of your favourite My Magic Pet Morphle episodes including 'Morphle Robs a Bank'.
Subscribe to Morphle TV Here: https://www.youtube.com/user/MagicPetsSongs4Kids?sub_confirmation=1

In this compilation of the My Magic Pet Morphle cartoon Morphle morphs into all sorts of things like a T-Rex, Dinosaurs, Triceratops,  an Ambulance, Monster Truck, a truck, a dump truck a fire truck, bus, a crane. other vehicles, dinosaurs, animals and a robot.

'My Magic Pet Morphle' is an animated hit tv show for toddlers and older kids. But because of it's fun colors and sounds it is even popular with babies. Morphle can morph into anything his human companion Mila wants. From dinosaus to cars, construction vehicles like diggers, dumptrucks and cranes to pets like cats dogs and lions!
